PSCT.Base: If this card is Normal or Special Summoned: You can Set 1 "Dinomorphia" Trap directly from your Deck to your Spell & Trap Zone, then if your LP are 2000 or less, this card gains 500 ATK. You can only use each effect of "Dinomorphia Therizia" once per turn.
